Rodmius was distracted. As if out of no where he was behind him. His tail 
quickly wrapping around him pining his arms to his sides. Galvatron wispered 
into Rodimus's ears. "I missed you my young nemisis. You have something I 
want. I will not kill you now weres the fun in that? O But pain thats  
another story." He placed his hand on his lower back and fired a laser shot  
to create a wound large enough to make some incredible pain. He then 
realeased and as fast as he was there he tranformed into his dragon mode and 
jetted off. Proto stood shaking at the sigh of his former ruler.

--part1_12.21a0407e.2a5538cf_boundary
